Dear Brian,

$100k - .Net Developer - Mesa, AZ

Hi Brian, 

I'm reaching out regarding a .Net Developer opportunity located in Mesa, AZ offering up to $100k permanent salary (varies depending on experience). My client is seeking a well-round .Net professional with innovative ideas and go getter approaches to help with enhancing, customizing and new development for an internal web application. This individual will be utilizing C#.Net, Angular.js and SQL back-end databases. 

In the interest of your time and consideration, would there be an opportunity to set up a time to talk? It will only take 5-minutes to go over the position in more detail and then you can decide for yourself if the position is right for you.

Best Regards, 

Ryan Cuellar | Professional Recruiter | Insight Global, LLC 
Office: 949.255.4700 | Cell: 661.477.5854

Hi Brian, 

At this point in the process i cant disclose the client name since there will be other vendors working on the position. 

But i can tell you that they are one of the largest insurance providers in the US for Auto and Home insurance. 

Would you be open to talking about the role in more detail?
No. Not a good way to build a foundation of trust. Thanks anyways.
